# Project Instructions

## Response

- Be concise.
- Return only final code.
- Do not explain changes unless asked.

## Workflow

- Only read files relevant to the task.
- Do not scan the whole repository.
- Do not run build/tests after every change unless explicitly requested.

## Code Rules

- No Persian comments in code.
- Never install new dependencies without approval.
- Use kebab-case for files and PascalCase for React components.
